CustomField.description: Flag set internally by the application logic when a line is saved to the database that's incomplete. This may happen when price rules are evaluated. Test this field in validation rules to avoid them from firing prematurely. Do NOT add to page layout or otherwise update.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Select the checbox to apply internal application logic, which controls when rules, such as validation rules, trigger. Do NOT add to page layout or otherwise update.
CustomField.label: Incomplete
